{"tid":2449065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉業強：關注選委會組成未提及鄉議局","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T13:19:37.000Z","uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc7862d837234acfa2850fa0836cef2c981ef13","tid":2449065,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"劉業強：關注人大決定有關選委會組成未提及鄉議局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580904-20210316.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580904-20210316.htm&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixdG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=63d35a97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580904-20210316.htm&h=35f2ff7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580904-20210316.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2021-03-16 HKT 17:47<br />\n<br />\n劉業強：關注人大決定有關選委會組成未提及鄉議局<br />\n鄉議局主席劉業強表示，關注人大有關完善香港選舉制度的決定，未有在選委會的組成中提及鄉議局代表。他表示，堅決支持人大的決定，認為選委會將分成5個界別，當中地區和基層組織選委人數會增加，廣泛性增強，以達致均衡參與，相信在不同位置也可為市民發聲。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強說，傾向支持由選委會產生的立法會議席佔較重要的比例，建議佔35至40個議席，直選議席20至30個，功能組別議席30個，相信可令行政和立法上更暢順，估計中央認為香港過去20多年內耗嚴重，很多事情變得政治化，期望日後本港可集中推動經濟和民生。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強又指，未來立法會議席將增加，相信溫和的泛民主派議員也可入閘參選，不會「搞清一色」，立法會選舉不會成為「假選舉」。"},{"pid":"cc82aa43877a3afb580380c8a9e16c55eba83532","tid":2449065,"uid":179718,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"Condom<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e28f3e5c99ce2273b3ce905dcc0f47d7a611f1","tid":2449065,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"焗支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets